Try this:

(9) -> for i in 0..7 repeat output(i::String,x^i)
   0 1
   1 %A
       2
   2 %A
   3 %A + 1
       2
   4 %A  + %A
       2
   5 %A  + %A + 1
       2
   6 %A  + 1
   7 1
                                                   Type: Void

Regards,
Bill Page.



